<p class="graytext" style="margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 35px;">
<p class="graytext">Ryan Bradley, ND, MPH is a doctor of naturopathic medicine in Seattle, WA. Diabetes is an area of both research and clinical specialization for Dr. Bradley. He practices integrative care for diabetes and heart health as the Director of the Center for Diabetes & Cardiovascular Wellness at the <a href="http://www.bastyr.edu/" target="_blank">Bastyr University</a></p>

<p>Bill Walter, ND is a doctor of naturopathic medicine in Eugene, OR.  He practices privately at the Golden Apple Healthcare clinic: <a href="http://www.goldenapplehealthcare.com" target="_blank">www.goldenapplehealthcare.com.</a> He provides naturopathic primary care for adults, with a special focus on chronic pain, cardiovascular and diabetes wellness, and allergic conditions.</p>


<p style="margin-left: 150px;"><img src="../images/content/pagebuilder/12936.jpg" alt="Complementary Corner" /><a class="subheading" href="PageNavigator/Complementary%20Corner/complementary"> View other Complementary Corner topics</a></p>
